p>\r\n              <p>\r\n                <button class=\"single_add_to_cart_button button\">\r\n                  Buy Now\r\n                </button>\r\n              </p>\r\n            </a>\r\n            <p>\r\n              <a\r\n                href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene-hydrance-intense-hydrating-serum-30ml/\"\r\n              ></a>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <p>\r\n            Infused with <strong>Avène</strong> thermal spring water,\r\n            <strong>Avène Hydrance Intense Hydrating Serum</strong> provides the\r\n            skin with a boost of hydration, leaving the skin plump and supple.\r\n            The light serum texture is easily absorbed and sinks comfortably\r\n            into the skin, providing instant relief from dryness and leaving the\r\n            skin fresh, luminous, and radiant throughout the day.\r\n          </p>\r\n          <hr />\r\n          <p>\r\n            Well, now that you’ve seen our selection of the best\r\n            <strong>Avène</strong> products out there, we hope you’ve found the\r\n            right one for you. Looking for something else? Then don’t hesitate\r\n            to\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.caretobeauty.com/avene/\">browse the full <strong>Avène</strong> skincare range here</a>.\r\n          </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>', '2022-04-01'),
